17
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,000
Kev, come on. Hustle.

18
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:04,000
You are murdering the Nardoc!

19
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:08,000
This is Kevin. Please hold and I will transfer you.

20
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,000
